<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Speyer</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen des Kürschners Hans Jung, Bürger zu Speyer, mit, dass Hans Sachsenfelder, Bürger zu Nürnberg, die Stadt verlassen hatte und man dem Boten aus Speyer nach Rückkehr des Hans Sachsenfelder Ladung vor das Gericht wegen der schuldigen fünf Gulden zugesagt hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_219" id="109r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l9">Speyr </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l10"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Hanſen <expan>Jung<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>kürſn<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> <expan>mitb<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l12"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / dem Hans <expan>Sachſenfeld<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l11"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab></add> ſchuldig ſey fünf <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> / . <expan>Denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l13">brief <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> ewr bote <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>meiſt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough">ch</del> am Suntag <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l14">abend / . vnd ſchickt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>germeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> nach <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Sachſenfelfeld<ex>er</ex></expan> / vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> des </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l15">
<del rend="strikethrough">kund man nicht vinden / wan er als vnd er ewrs vo </del> wolt mit Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l16">geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Da vand man ſein nicht / . vnd do 
<del rend="strikethrough"> hieʒʒ </del> redt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l17"><expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>meiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Er ſolt Jm des montags 
<del rend="strikethrough"> and </del> an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l18">frawen tag des nachts <expan>fürbıet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / ſo wolt man Jm des <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l19">auf den dinſtag frü als hewt helffen / . Alſo ſagt man daʒ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l20">Sachſenfelder hin weck wer / 
<del rend="strikethrough">da </del> vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> wer er hie heim <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l22">alſo weıſten wir den <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ er <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> wirt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l21">bey vns </ab></add> / dıe klage <expan>aufgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l23">hat / vnd <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> er herheim kümt ſo <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> wirt / an des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l26"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ſtat des <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_219_line_1576592788900_5509">von Jm </ab></add> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen / vnd <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jm auch des <expan>yecʒund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l27"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>geholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> wer <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Sachſe </del> het er den <expan>Sachſenfeld<ex>er</ex></expan> mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l28">fürpot <expan>begrıffe<ex>n</ex></expan> / wan wo etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vts<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_219" id="109r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Speyr </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                                von Hansen <expan>Jung<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>kürsn<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>mitb<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>,
                                                  <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, dem Hans
                                                  <expan>Sachsenfeld<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                                  <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan></add>, schuldig sey
                                                fünf <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                                                  <expan>Denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief
                                                  <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> ewr bote
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>meist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date">am suntag <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen
                                            abend</q>01.02.1411</note></app>; und schickt <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>germeist<ex>er</ex></expan> nach
                                                  <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>Sachsenfeld<ex>er</ex></expan> und wolt mit
                                                im geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, da vand man
                                                sein nicht. Und do redt
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>meist<ex>er</ex></expan>
                                                mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, er solt im des
                                          <app><note><q type="date">montags an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag</q>02.02.1411</note></app>
                                                des nachts <expan>fürbiet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so
                                                wolt man im des <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auf
                                                den dinstag frü als hewt helffen. Also sagt man, daz
                                                der Sachsenfelder hin weck wer, und also weisten wir
                                                den <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz er
                                                  <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> wirt <add>bey
                                                  uns</add> die klage
                                                  <expan>aufgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, und
                                                  <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> er herheim kümt, so
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                                  <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> wirt an des
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> stat des
                                                  <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>von im</add>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen und
                                                  <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> im auch des
                                                  <expan>yeczund<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>geholffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, het er den
                                                  <expan>Sachsenfeld<ex>er</ex></expan> mit
                                                  <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> fürpot
                                                  <expan>begriffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, wan wo etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ut s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
